title: Vertiv Avocent ACS 8000: CPU temperature
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/vertiv
license: GPL
distribution: kuhn-ruess
description:
 Reads the internal CPU temperature of a Vertiv Avocent ACS 8000 from
 acsSensorsInternalCurrentCPUTemperature ({.1.3.6.1.4.1.10418.26.2.7.1.0}),
 reported in degrees Celsius.

 Upper temperature levels default to 70 °C (WARN) and 85 °C (CRIT) and can
 be adjusted via the WATO ruleset {Vertiv ACS CPU temperature}.

 Performance data:
  - {temp} (CPU temperature in °C)

inventory:
 A single service per host is created.
